    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3335054>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–5. General morphology of adult Phyllogomphoides spp. 1) Head, frontal view, P. nayaritensis, female; 2) Head, dorsal view P. apiculatus, female; 3) Thorax, left lateral view P. nayaritensis, male; 4) Thorax, left lateral view P. pugnifer, male; 5) Anterior and posterior wings P. pacificus, male." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3335054/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3335056>
    dc:description "FIGURES 6–10. Details of the abdomen of Phyllogomphoides spp. 6) Abdominal segments S8–10 and foliations, left lateral view P. albrighti, male; 7) Abdominal segments S8–10 and foliations, left lateral view P. duodentatus, male; 8) Accessory genitalia, ventral view P. albrighti, male; 9) Accessory genitalia, ventral view P. pacificus, male. 10) Accessory genitalia, ventral view P. apiculatus, male." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3335056/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3335068>
    dc:description "FIGURES 43–52. Male accessory genitalia, ventral and ventrolateral view. 43–44) P. albrighti; 45–46) P. apiculatus; 47–48) P. bifasciatus; 49–50) P. danieli; 51–52) P. duodentatus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3335068/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3335070>
    dc:description "FIGURES 53–62. Male accessory genitalia, ventral and ventrolateral view. 53–54) P. enriquei; 55–56) P. indicatrix (alcoholic teneral specimen); 57–58) P. luisi; 59–60) P. nayaritensis; 61–62) P. pacificus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3335070/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3335072>
    dc:description "FIGURES 63–68. Male accessory genitalia, ventral and ventrolateral view. 63–64) P. pugnifer; 65–66) P. stigmatus; 67–68) P. suasus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3335072/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3335058>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11–16. Details of the abdomen of Phyllogomphoides spp. 11) Caudal appendages, dorsal view P. pacificus, male; 12) Caudal appendages, dorsal view P. duodentatus, male; 13) Caudal appendages, dorsolateral view P. pacificus, male; 14) Caudal appendages, dorsolateral view P. albrighti, male; 15) Vulvar lamina, ventral view P. luisi, female; 16) Vulvar lamina, lateroventral view P. duodentatus, female." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3335058/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

